r.<br>
<br>
A lot of people on this page have said over and over that they work before lvl 34, but you don't get the new graphic until lvl 34.  All you get is some stats bonuses, which can be really helpful.  I konw that I started my quests at lvl 16, and as soon as I got my focus items I tried every lvl of pet, but didn't notice a size difference in the lower ones.  Against a mage pet of the same lvl, the focused ones would win more times than not due to the minor stat increases.<br>
<br>
At least, this is what I have found and seen, but try casting them again, and making sure you are looking at the pets using the same view.  You will probably see that they are the same size, but I am going back and trying this when I log on next just to see if they changed the graphic for lvl 16 pets (focused vs unfocuses).<br>
